galaxytool:concoct a schema:SoftwareApplication ;
    schema:applicationSubCategory edam:topic_3174 ;
    schema:description "CONCOCT (Clustering cONtigs with COverage and ComposiTion) does unsupervised binning of metagenomic contigs byusing nucleotide composition - kmer frequencies - and coverage data for multiple samples. CONCOCT can accurately(up to species level) bin metagenomic contigs." ;
